item.title: McLaren park downed tree
item.author: Jesse Bounds
item.description: We’ve seen a lot of intense winter storms in San Francisco this year. The rain has kept the ground soft and the heavy wind has taken down a lot of trees. In McLaren Park, several of the trees have fallen over the Philosopher’s Way trail.
